OL,3,C'I miss my homeland': Iranian living
OL,4,Cin Bolton hopes strikes lead to change
OL,6,FHourdad Naserpour told ITV News how
OL,7,Fconflicted he feels about the strikes
OL,8,Fagainst the Iranian regime and his
OL,9,Fhopes to return home.
OL,11,FAn Iranian man who is unable to return
OL,12,Fto his homeland hopes the unrest in
OL,13,Fhis country, which has claimed the
OL,14,Flives of a dozen of friends, will lead
OL,15,Fto lasting change.
OL,17,FHourdad Naserpour, 33, moved to the UK
OL,18,Fin 2015 and lives in Bolton, but has
OL,19,Fnot been back to Iran in over a decade
OL,20,Fbecause he converted to Christianity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
