OL,3,C'I miss my homeland': Iranian living
OL,4,Cin Bolton hopes strikes lead to change
OL,6,FIn Iran, changing one's faith from
OL,7,FIslam is treated as a grave offence
OL,8,Fthat can carry the death penalty.
OL,10,FHe said: "I became a Christian, and
OL,11,Fchanging your belief and religion in
OL,12,FIran is not a simple and personal
OL,13,Fdecision. I could be persecuted,
OL,14,Ftortured, and in some cases even lose
OL,15,Fmy life."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
