PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772565071
OL,3,C'I miss my homeland': Iranian living
OL,4,Cin Bolton hopes strikes lead to change
OL,6,FThe 33-year-old says he has been
OL,7,F"unable to sleep" as he watches
OL,8,FAmerican and Israeli forces carry out
OL,9,Fairstrikes on his country over the
OL,10,Flast four days, in an attempt to
OL,11,Ftopple the current regime.
OL,13,FAt least 787 people in Iran have been
OL,14,Fkilled in US-Israeli airstrikes since
OL,15,FSaturday, according to the Iranian Red
OL,16,FCrescent Society.
OL,18,FTrump said the US military was
OL,19,F"knocking the crap" out of Iran in an
OL,20,Finterview with ITV News' US partner
OL,21,FCNN late on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772565071
OL,3,C'I miss my homeland': Iranian living
OL,4,Cin Bolton hopes strikes lead to change
OL,6,FHourdad said: "It's so complicated...
OL,7,Fyour country is being attacked, the
OL,8,Fstreets you grew up in are being
OL,9,Fbombed, but you have just a little bit
OL,10,Fof hope that it could lead to freedom.
OL,12,F"No one is approving the war, but if
OL,13,Fit's the only way to help my people
OL,14,Fthen that is what I want.
OL,16,F"For years there have been
OL,17,Fnegotiations and talks but at the end
OL,18,Fof it was nothing but the deaths of
OL,19,FIranians. It's not the war we are
OL,20,Fcelebrating, it's the hope that it
OL,21,Fcould lead to our freedom."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
