PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772565071
OL,3,C'I miss my homeland': Iranian living
OL,4,Cin Bolton hopes strikes lead to change
OL,6,FThe airstrikes come just weeks after a
OL,7,Fseries of protests across Iran against
OL,8,Fthe current regime, which were quelled
OL,9,Fwhen an estimated 30,000 people were
OL,10,Fkilled in the streets, according to
OL,11,Fthe country's Ministry of Health.
OL,13,FAmong the dead were a number of
OL,14,FHourdad's friends.
OL,16,FHe said: "When the uprising started
OL,17,Fthey turned the internet off for a few
OL,18,Fdays and then the first news I saw on
OL,19,Fsocial media after the shutdown was
OL,20,Fpictures of my close friends being
OL,21,Fkilled.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772565071
OL,3,C'I miss my homeland': Iranian living
OL,4,Cin Bolton hopes strikes lead to change
OL,6,F"People that would say to me 'one day
OL,7,Fyou will come back to a free Iran and
OL,8,Fwe will be together' but now even if I
OL,9,Ffly back tomorrow there are people I
OL,10,Fwill never see again.
OL,12,F"I've lost about 13 friends over the
OL,13,Flast few weeks."
OL,15,FThe recent US-Isreali airstrikes have
OL,16,Ftargeted a number of high ranking
OL,17,Fofficials in the Iranian regime,
OL,18,Fincluding the Supreme Leader Ali
OL,19,FKhamenei.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772565071
OL,3,C'I miss my homeland': Iranian living
OL,4,Cin Bolton hopes strikes lead to change
OL,6,FHourdad said: "As a Christian, I don't
OL,7,Fcelebrate death but I do celebrate
OL,8,FGod's justice.
OL,10,F"But we need to understand that it
OL,11,Fwasn't just one individual person that
OL,12,Foppressed people for many years. When
OL,13,Fyou hear the mothers crying, the
OL,14,Ffathers crying, brothers and sisters
OL,15,Fcrying, grieving for their loved ones,
OL,16,Fwe need to make sure that is about an
OL,17,Fend to that ideology, not just endless
OL,18,Fescalation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772565071
OL,3,C'I miss my homeland': Iranian living
OL,4,Cin Bolton hopes strikes lead to change
OL,6,F"So what people are celebrating is an
OL,7,Fend of the chapter of long suffering
OL,8,Ffor many years. They are celebrating
OL,9,Fthe beginning for them of this long
OL,10,Fjourney and long road to freedom. And
OL,11,Fthey're hoping that they get to the
OL,12,Fend of that road so they can see that
OL,13,Ffreedom."
OL,15,FFor Hourdad, the recent military
OL,16,Faction has allowed him to think about
OL,17,Freturning home for the first time in
OL,18,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1772565071
OL,3,C'I miss my homeland': Iranian living
OL,4,Cin Bolton hopes strikes lead to change
OL,6,FHe said: "I've been waiting for that
OL,7,Fmoment for 11 years and now it looks
OL,8,Flike I could go home one day.
OL,10,F"One thing I realised in the last few
OL,11,Fweeks is the love I have for my
OL,12,Fhomeland. I just miss my people, and I
OL,13,Fjust want to hug every single person.
OL,15,F"Just thinking about it makes my heart
OL,16,Fbeat faster and tears come to my eyes.
OL,18,F"I have no words to explain how much I
OL,19,Fmiss my homeland, how much I miss
OL,20,Fbreathing in that air and walking
OL,21,Fthose streets."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
